comments.body:
Tbh , in my opinion even if you get placed for 12LPA , the return of investment isn't going to be a lot .... you really need to consider your options. If you are getting even getting ise in bms or msrit my opinion would be to take it . CSE in BIT/DSCE are not bad options either , many of my friends have been placed well in top companies like amazon/goldman sachs through these colleges .

&#x200B;

Also there is barely any college life in pes lmao , its the same race as you had during jee/neet but just on a smaller scale.
